{"tid":555724,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"夜深了 你有否想起他/她","createTime":"2018-02-09T17:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T15:12:43.000Z","uid":89134,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e41a1ce8a6939031eedd5fc5f469d11abeb448","tid":555724,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T17:42:12.000Z","msg":"每一晚<br />\n你地都會傾Wtsapp 煲電話粥<br />\n一齊傾通宵 講完早抖都唔知點解又講多兩個幾鐘<br />\n不停地sd 好掛住你 既字眼 好似中咗毒咁 不能抽離<br />\n每一分每一秒都想見到對方<br />\n<br />\n唔想比人發現或者嘈到屋企人 你會壓低你既聲線 <br />\n果種感覺好似偷情咁 好甜蜜 好快樂<br />\n但係而家你唔會再壓低你既聲線 你只係好想大聲咁叫佢既名 哀求佢返嚟你身邊為止 控訴佢既不忠/不負責任/離開<br />\n<br />\n每一晚<br />\n你會係Wts app check佢幾時上線 想打電話比佢 <br />\n但又發現你既身分似乎不對 想傳一個訊息比佢<br />\n但又欲言又止 知道咁樣做只係犯賤 佢已經唔愛你 唔會返嚟你身邊<br />\n即使你掛住、深愛住佢好似中咗毒咁 擁有解藥既佢都唔會回頭看你一眼"},{"pid":"42fecc214e098ca2290fa4830bf034a2a837ab68","tid":555724,"uid":43196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OOEC34Ndb1o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOOEC34Ndb1o&d=aIZMRU5ExBvnv7AKmHg6R5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=1bbb1ffa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OOEC34Ndb1o</a><br />\n如果可以時光倒流<br />\n我希望同你無識過，咩都無發生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f7ff6fa37351d4e9e050e59c73158162ba69dd","tid":555724,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42fecc214e098ca2290fa4830bf034a2a837ab68","tid":555724,"uid":43196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OOEC34Ndb1o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOOEC34Ndb1o&d=aIZMRU5ExBvnv7AKmHg6R5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=1bbb1ffa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OOEC34Ndb1o</a><br />\n如果可以時光倒流<br />\n我希望同你無識過，咩都無發生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T17:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji